{"tid":1554296,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"彭斯今年秋季將就中国問題發表重要講話","createTime":"2019-09-09T02:12:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-09T02:14:53.000Z","uid":184679,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"2c15fe4fec7e244b40f9efcad654eccb2a366520","tid":1554296,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T02:12:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.hkej.com/hkej/images/2019/09/07/2245157_2eaa4f4338064b195ae47e63d0837b2d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.hkej.com%2Fhkej%2Fimages%2F2019%2F09%2F07%2F2245157_2eaa4f4338064b195ae47e63d0837b2d.jpg&h=5b75e6b6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國副總統彭斯就中國問題的重要講話，由原定6月押後到今年稍後，預料講話會嚴厲批評中國。<br />\n<br />\n彭斯新聞秘書指出，講話會在今年秋季發表，但無具體日期。消息人士稱，講話的基調會按發表時，美中兩國關係是好是壞而決定。<br />\n<br />\n彭斯原定在6月的講話，適逢總統特朗普和中國國家主席習近平在大阪二十國集團(G20)峰會會面前，故為了製造兩國元首的對話氣份，彭斯的講話須押後。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2245157/%E5%BD%AD%E6%96%AF%E4%BB%8A%E5%B9%B4%E7%A7%8B%E5%AD%A3%E5%B0%87%E5%B0%B1%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%95%8F%E9%A1%8C%E7%99%BC%E8%A1%A8%E9%87%8D%E8%A6%81%E8%AC%9B%E8%A9%B1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fcurrent%2Farticle%2F2245157%2F%25E5%25BD%25AD%25E6%2596%25AF%25E4%25BB%258A%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E7%25A7%258B%25E5%25AD%25A3%25E5%25B0%2587%25E5%25B0%25B1%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%2595%258F%25E9%25A1%258C%25E7%2599%25BC%25E8%25A1%25A8%25E9%2587%258D%25E8%25A6%2581%25E8%25AC%259B%25E8%25A9%25B1&d=uCl2s%2BJteilWOEmp%2BZl8kd9AtAt3lYzSqFOpIRNeugk%3D&h=61108164\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2245157/%E5%BD%AD%E6%96%AF%E4%BB%8A%E5%B9%B4%E7%A7%8B%E5%AD%A3%E5%B0%87%E5%B0%B1%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%95%8F%E9%A1%8C%E7%99%BC%E8%A1%A8%E9%87%8D%E8%A6%81%E8%AC%9B%E8%A9%B1</a>"},{"pid":"597b916535a4228d3a41ac996916d9d8eb785b67","tid":1554296,"uid":118322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T02:13:59.000Z"